                       for Windows)  includes capabilities similar to SureMath. 
 
 
 
 
 Only identify what is asked for. Ignore all the ifs, ands and buts.... 
 A problem is understood by solving it not by pondering it. 
 
	 
		 
			
			 
				 
					 
						 
