			These problems provide the background in problem solving needed to solve problems reliably in more advanced courses. They provide the edge needed to excel in all courses and tests involving use of mathematics in problem solving at the elementary, high school and university levels. 
			 
				Change 
			 
			the way you solve problems forever! Break the problem solving barrier and make 
			
				Story Problems 
			
			fun and a constructive learning experience by moving past pretend-a-math. 
		 
	 
 

    
		 
		
		
